data.description: Welcome to 67 Lake View Loop in the exclusive gated section, The Lakes of Cross Creek Ranch. This waterfront home features 3 bedrooms, 2 full & 1 half baths, & 3 car garage. Come inside & find rich wood flooring throughout most of the home. Your kitchen has a wrap-around raised breakfast-bar, center island, dual ovens, stainless steel appliances, water filtration at the sink, & under cabinet lighting. Your primary bedroom has lake views right from your windows & an en suite with dual sinks, separate shower with bench, whirlpool bath w/showerhead, sky lights for natural light, & walk-in closet w/custom storage. This home also has a dedicated office w/glass French doors, wood floors, & tray ceilings. Head outside & find a big covered patio w/built-in grill & a huge yard w/water views! Fall in love w/Cross Creek Ranch which features miles of walking & biking trails, multiple resort style pools, community restaurant & gym, & natural landscaping to bring you closer to the wild Texas beauty.
